Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.07,0:02:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,抵消冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.71,0:02:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.78,0:02:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,次元具现化
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.17,0:02:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,烦死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.64,0:02:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.84,0:03:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,真的只是看着就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.61,0:03:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 只不过是Λ的启动测试而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你待机就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 刚才是不是有什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.71,0:03:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道 是不是在施工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.33,0:03:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定是拉格纳先生...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,谁管那种萝莉控啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.80,0:03:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,疼疼 我还没完全恢复呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你还真敢干啊 ν
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.87,0:03:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 不攻过来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就不客气了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 Λ 干掉那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.79,0:04:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,拉... {\alpha&HFF&}格... 纳...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,拉... 格... {\alpha&HFF&}纳...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,拉... 格... 纳...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.00,0:04:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.07,0:04:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然还有μ-13 的记忆？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,帝卡 传送Λ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.09,0:04:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.18,0:04:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 乱差使别人的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}赤鬼{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.26,0:04:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.65,0:04:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,拉格纳·布拉德艾奇 九重让我传话给你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.44,0:04:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,说: "感谢你的帮忙"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,帮忙？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在打什么主意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.16,0:04:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,九重做的事 我也搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,一个个都这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到还留有μ-13 的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.75,0:05:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是 {\i1}Life Link{\i0}? 的影响吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.86,0:05:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,看来需要重新调整了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不认识啊 你去问问其他人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎! 欢迎!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.21,0:05:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,都是好东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.84,0:05:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶 明明应该就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,发现如月琴恩阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,在下 叫做万驱·狮子神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:05:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我脸上的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,您不会是忘记了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,哼 斑鸠的逃亡者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,主公的仇 就让我来讨还吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,试试看吧
